data.title: What is the SWASH® 10-Minute Clothing Care System?
data.description: The SWASH® System is the only in-home 10-minute express clothing care system. It's designed to fit your life, so you can say goodbye to excessive washing, drying, ironing, and dry cleaning.

data.title: Get to know SWASH® 10-Minute Clothing Care
data.description: From Whirlpool and Tide comes the revolutionary SWASH® System. Get acquainted with the system and learn how it works, all the ways it will let you save, and how it cares for clothes that aren’t quite ready to be washed or taken to the dry cleaner. Find more about this innovative technology at SWASH.com
